  "description": {
   "en": "A comet falling will bring about a great calamity, and in order to choose a child fated by the falling comet, the family of the \"Reiken\" clan with a long storied history is once again resuming its entrance examination process to find disciples. The protagonist Ōriku (Lu Wang in the original novel), who possesses a special soul that only appears once in a thousand years, decides to take the exam, and he starts down the path toward becoming an exceptional sage.  \r\n  \r\nThe links are to AnimeNewsNetwork for the anime:  \r\n[Season 1](https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=17829)  \r\n[Season 2](https://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=18800)"
